---
title: Pear & Broccolini Salad with Parmesan, Mint & Pine Nuts | Serves 2
description: Everyone needs a go-to green salad in their repertoire, just like this one. The sweetness of pear, crunch of pine nuts, peppery kick of rocket and sharpness of Parmesan bring plenty of flavour and texture, but it's still super-easy to pull together.
